<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mkẖlṣy bạlnʿmẗ whbtny ạlyqyn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mukẖalĩṣī biạlnĩʿ̊maẗi
 wahab̊tanī ạl̊yaqīn̊
 kāltẖãl̊ji ṣir̊tu ṭāhiraⁿạ
 bidamika ạltẖãmīn̊

[V2]
 2- laqad̊ nazaʿ̊ta lilạảbad̊
 ại̹tẖ̊mī wāảtẖ̊qālī
 waṣir̊ta lī niʿ̊ma ạlsãnad̊
 wafīka ậmālī

[V3]
 3- biạldãmi qad̊ qanaẙtanī
 mutã lạảḥ̊yā fīk̊
 faṣir̊tu ʿab̊daⁿạ muq̊tanay̱
 kulã ạltẖãnā ạủh̊dīk̊

[V4]
 4- damuⁿ wamāʾuⁿ jarayā
 min̊ jan̊bika ạl̊maj̊rūḥ̊
 fadaẙtanī ṭahãr̊tanī
 kẖatam̊tanī biạlrũwḥ̊

[V5]
 5- kulũ ạn̊tiẓārī sayĩdī
 mal̊qāka fī ạl̊maj̊di
 fālrũwḥu ʿur̊būnuⁿ walaẘ
 ạủz̊raʿu fī ạllãḥ̊di

[V6]
 6- yā lasurūrī ại̹dẖ̊ ạảray̱
 waj̊haka yā ḥabīb̊
 ạảkūnu mitẖ̊laka ại̹dẖaⁿạ
 fī ạl̊maj̊di ʿan̊ qarīb̊</lyrics>
<author>jwn nywtn</author>
</song>